The paper proposes a novel approach that combines Long Short-Term Memory networks and Graph Convolutional Networks to learn long short-term dependencies together with graph structure. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
